  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765221517\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/444a9f334268c872db16a621263f7330.avif?t=1765221517\" width=610 height=302 /></span><br>In the game you have to line up three crystals in a row by rotating the level and jumping.<br><br>Feature of game:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Adventure with the rotation of the level<br></li><li>Collect crystals and coins<br></li><li>Convenient control<br></li><li>Challenging levels<br></li><li>Physics<br></li><li>Traps.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/68c20d7fba33f25484ffb3a763a0ad2f.poster.avif?t=1765221517\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/68c20d7fba33f25484ffb3a763a0ad2f.webm?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/68c20d7fba33f25484ffb3a763a0ad2f.mp4?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Line up three crystals in one line and collect points to go to the next level!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b09127e097e48b0a065801e2f94c4b32.poster.avif?t=1765221517\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b09127e097e48b0a065801e2f94c4b32.webm?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1475150/extras/b09127e097e48b0a065801e2f94c4b32.mp4?t=1765221517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
